cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about unsupervised learning of visual features using clustering methods applied to convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel method for jointly learning the parameters of the neural network and the cluster assignments, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Finally, the paper applies the method to large datasets, which could also fall under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
